data.description: Absolutely spotless . The only way to explain this home. Starting with the long driveway to keep your cars safe, then you enter the home and WOW. Talk about ready to move into. And the room sizes. The kitchen with all new appliances and looking into the backyard desert oasis. Then hear upstairs and the large loft welcomes you. Laundry room is actually a room and then BOOM. The primary bedroom with the hug sitting area and a large bathroom. I mean. Sheds and backyard fridge included in sale What else could you ask for.WELCOME HOME ..YES. WELCOME HOME
